(Mac not supported), requires iOS 10.2+ version. The package comes with a phone stand so that you can clamp your phone into a horizontal view (phone clamp only for iPhone or iPod size only, maximum 3 inch width). Also the gamepad can be used with drone, helicopter or other wireless game toy devices.|[HIGH QUALITY JOYPAD] The joystick paint high quality rubber oil, special finish on surface for consistent grip when playing, give you comfortable and smooth feel , antiperspirant and non-slip, durable and no scratches, perfect fit with the finger, let you do a job with skill and ease control. F-sence: pressure sensitive buttons offer precise control and accurate response, perfect real action play with real games and strong feeling. Get charged about 2 hours and can play 24-30 hours.');
